TIER 3 — POLYMARKET-SPECIFIC TOOLING
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Official SDKs (for reference and prototyping):
  TypeScript: @polymarket/clob-client (npm)
              Install: npm install @polymarket/clob-client ethers
  Python:     py-clob-client (pypi)
              Install: pip install py-clob-client

IMPORTANT: There is NO official Rust SDK for Polymarket as of 2026.
Our Rust engine implements the CLOB protocol from scratch using:
  - reqwest for REST calls
  - tokio-tungstenite for WebSocket
  - alloy for EIP-712 signing

